{"tid":2085564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共匪：應速推明日大嶼 效法英國玫瑰園計畫 撤資前撈最後一筆","createTime":"2020-06-30T02:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T02:53:48.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1efc4ca3292647b52b051a5e524ac5a527324d","tid":2085564,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:37:25.000Z","msg":"陳家駒：政府應拿出勇氣推動「明日大嶼」<br />\n30.06.2020 10:30<br />\n<br />\n建造業議會主席陳家駒發表網誌，提到前港督衛奕信在1989年香港出現信心危機時，果斷拍板「玫瑰園計劃」，興建赤鱲角機場、青嶼幹線等多項核心項目，以基建推動經濟，為香港再起飛帶來新動力。他指出，經過整整一年的人禍天災及內憂外患，本港各行各業正面對前所未有的挑戰，需要一個比「玫瑰園」更玫瑰的項目，協助香港衝出陰霾，他認為特首在2018年提出「明日大嶼」，正是解決香港問題的希望，政府需要拿出勇氣，迎難而上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1324732&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1324732%26csid%3D261_341&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=c5d2cf71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1324732&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"75f0d0119caeb60b7f84163594248dca43b5bf09","tid":2085564,"uid":115579,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"搶埋庫房最後一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2902c7a8db2230167e937ac889e7e9ebb3e603d1","tid":2085564,"uid":59868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"使咩勇氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有果班忠誠勇毅係到<br />\n邊個反對拉邊個，告佢癲覆國家<br />\n想解釋？有咩同個紅官講"},{"pid":"9bdc0ceec43afd6df86e1940cc169ea5b3ab5210","tid":2085564,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"Lol"},{"pid":"33753930fc98cc7a47eece8c72290c481f700629","tid":2085564,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"點解